item.title: Middle Earth with Connie Gibbs and Delia Gallegos
item.description:
Moiya is joined by fellow nerds Connie Gibbs and Delia Gallegos to discuss the worldbuilding in Tolkien's Lord of the Rings! There is so much to unpack, from the creation of the world, origin of its magic, Tolkien's inspirations, and the little matter of having a FLAT WORLD!

HOSTED by Dr. Moiya McTier (@GoAstroMo), astrophysicist and folklorist

GUESTS

  • Connie Gibbs is a nerd, writer, and social media manager for Scholastic. Find her on twitter at @Constar24... Feed: https://feeds.captivate.fm/exolore/
